Quickstrike:




Quickstrike made an outside check for Megatron, and no sign. He went 
back to the inside of the ship, angry. He was mad that Megatron 
escaped and Hell Beast was back. It truely wasn't happy about Hell 
Beast being in the ship. He never liked him. He was a reason why he 
couldn't stay still.

He walked to the room where the majoritry where the others were. He 
saw Hell Beast there. He leaned agianst the frame of the door and 
eyed him, arms crossed.
